<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Oop on siliconsenthil</title><link>https://siliconsenthil.in/categories/oop/</link><description>Recent content in Oop on siliconsenthil</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 15 Apr 2011 15:59:00 +0530</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://siliconsenthil.in/categories/oop/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>If else or Switch case to Polymorphism</title><link>https://siliconsenthil.in/blog/2011-04-15-if-else-or-switch-case-to-polymorphism/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 Apr 2011 15:59:00 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://siliconsenthil.in/blog/2011-04-15-if-else-or-switch-case-to-polymorphism/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;If you try to express your logic in if-else way like this,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; String &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getSoundIfElseWay&lt;/span&gt;(String animal) { 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (animal.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;equalsIgnoreCase&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Dog&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)) 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Bark&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (animal.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;equalsIgnoreCase&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Cat&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)) 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Mew&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (animal.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;equalsIgnoreCase&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Lion&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)) 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Roar&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; } 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;then polymorphic way would be,&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>